<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa gam ding lak guon khawvel ahin,
 Kei chieh zelingka ka puokgik tawh;
 Hun kilepsan hiel puongka Lal Isu;
 Melma dogal lien mahleh.

[V2]
 Gospel hehpih in malam zuon ka, (2)
 Ka Lal deihum min hawih hi panpih in,
 Tai puongka khawvel ma ah.

[V3]
 2. A nasep sunzawm zel ding kuo a um?
 Kei ei hun tel tai ka Lal Isu'n;
 Lawp takin Lalpa na chu semzel ka,
 Thih chana ginum dingin.

[V4]
 3. Malam ah kasep ding ei guotsak tai,
 Gospel henailo te pui dingin;
 Gitloh gallien chu kidopih zelin,
 Ei puihna phawtah chieh ka.

[V5]
 4. Aw hehpihna, Aw hehpihna mak chun,
 Ei sawldawk in khawigam himahleh;
 Muonna umloh na gamthip ahin le,
 Thim mahleh chieh zel ingka.</lyrics>
<title>Malam Zuon Zel Ka !</title>
</song>